data.description: Location is key for this urban farm. Sitting on .49 acre, this property has something for everyone. The fully brick home features a freshly painted interior, new LPV flooring throughout with beautiful porcelain tile in both bathrooms. In the kitchen you'll find an eat in area, new shaker style kitchen cabinet doors w/soft close, stainless appliances, gorgeous granite, a stylish backsplash, and color changing lights that also dim, just ask Alexa.  Cozy up to the gas fireplace in the living room w/a new stone tile surround. This home offers 4 beds & 2 baths with a split floor plan for optimal privacy. Outside indulge in the swimming pool complete with a slide & diving board, a fenced in garden area, a storage shed, a play set and a chicken pen with a run. This property is ideally located near Coler Mountain biking trail, 1/4 of a mile from Gateway Park, & near the new Wal Mart Campus. Come to be wowed by its beauty, find tranquility in the backyard oasis and love the convenience of this incredible location.
